{"tid":1487033,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[呢d咪做實事]數名市民政總請願　促林鄭請中央出動解放軍","createTime":"2019-08-19T05:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T17:03:27.000Z","uid":33775,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"1f14fadabb35b6d7c5cbc8ad28944c4c76c04888","tid":1487033,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/29b0b3f1-db3e-4e10-b80c-6a8c27ffe48f_I2XOp_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F29b0b3f1-db3e-4e10-b80c-6a8c27ffe48f_I2XOp_1200x0.png&h=f4ae91da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五名市民今早到金鐘政府總部請願，要求特首林鄭月娥依據《基本法》請中央政府派出駐港解放軍，維持社會治安。<br />\n<br />\n請願發起人藍雪寶自稱「土生土長香港人」，現職教師。她指近日警方執法備受制肘，眼見「暴亂」至今未能平息，故促請特首林鄭月娥要求駐港解放軍「止暴制亂，恢復秩序」。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣居住的藍雪寶，形容昨日由民陣舉行的「流水式」集會「非法」，參與者「漫無目的」在街上走，影響交通運作。她又形容示威者為「恐怖份子」，直斥他們「喪失理智」。她發現遊行當中皆有「外國人擔任指揮，與示威者一起打手勢」，故相信有外國勢力干預遊行。<br />\n<br />\n一行五人的請願人士揮動中國國旗，要求特首林鄭月娥依據《基本法》第十四條，請求中央政府派出駐港解放軍，以協助香港社會維持治安。按照《基本法》第十四條，中央政府派駐香港的軍隊不干預香港的地方事務，但港府在必要時，可向中央請求駐軍維持社會治安。一眾請願者最後向政府代表遞信，有請願者大喊：「繼續努力，玩殘佢哋（反送中示威者）！」<br />\n<br />\n同場，另有十名市民手持中國國旗和寫有「香港市民」標語，未有叫口號，僅在政府總部合照留影。被問及是否同行聲援，藍雪寶稱「唔識佢哋」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/hkhk_BQQUj_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhkhk_BQQUj_1200x0.jpeg&h=7c2437b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01896c8abc62f4a053b3c0a8341d9807e272bfda","tid":1487033,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">【雨傘2.0】劉業成有心公開銅鑼灣班卧底 就係想大家一齊捉鬼</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481711</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0321def928c4d6d6235991592753d41170bdf8ae","tid":1487033,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3280e88c557cd8b8e097a2aa6e858776726e00cc","tid":1487033,"uid":169665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:48:27.000Z","msg":"岩岩好10慢人做實事, 絕對支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0853f7af1d7c51b4127b13807cb854f621af95","tid":1487033,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"快出啦忍咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb2dcdd81dd6b7db67a50e0b8b1893d8ec6566b","tid":1487033,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"有無搞錯呀？咁大件事都唔上黎宣傳？一定好多人support你架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735324457fcfde015f7f777eff4e3b163bef40b5","tid":1487033,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"洪共政府點睇你地既支持者"},{"pid":"b01f01e8f7d27d2af3a1b04a8a681b0f42168008","tid":1487033,"uid":53954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:49:08.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n仲有用過琴日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fad122bfa19bbdc08b1fdf52ee4ec70e91ceb59","tid":1487033,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"成班騎呢怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14233a93247e333d1cec08360cb18bb6b83e9b5e","tid":1487033,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:49:31.000Z","msg":"<del>香港</del>中國市民"},{"pid":"583e56185d60aa0638e16d547b437fdd38199a05","tid":1487033,"uid":196450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"係就快"},